Currently our monthly spots are full but a spot comes open almost weekly.  In the mean time we suggest booking a weekly spot with us at $281/wk.  This will move you to the waitlist for monthly spots.  Monthly spots are $798 All Bills Paid for pull-through and $898 for back-ins.  Both require a full month of rent as a deposit in addition to rent.  This can later be applied to your last month’s rent or will be released to you when you move out.   All sites have 30 and 50 Amp hook ups and include fast internet with the price.  We do require a last month’s rent deposit or you can remain at the weekly rate of $281 as long as you want or until you have enough for the deposit!
